Sentencas: The heterointerface electrode, porous LaSrCoO4-delta on porous La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta, was examined by an ac impedance analysis.
Titulo: Composite Cathode of Perovskite-Related Oxides, (La,Sr)CoO3-δ/(La,Sr)2CoO4-δ, for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The performance of the heterointerface electrode was higher than those of LaSrCoO4-delta and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta.
Titulo: Composite Cathode of Perovskite-Related Oxides, (La,Sr)CoO3-δ/(La,Sr)2CoO4-δ, for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The better performance is attributed to the enhancement of oxygen surface reaction at the heterointerface of LaSrCoO4-delta and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta.
Titulo: Composite Cathode of Perovskite-Related Oxides, (La,Sr)CoO3-δ/(La,Sr)2CoO4-δ, for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results are consistent with high surface exchange coefficients at the heterointerface between LaSrCoO4-delta and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta, which were determined by oxygen isotope diffusion experiment.
Titulo: Composite Cathode of Perovskite-Related Oxides, (La,Sr)CoO3-δ/(La,Sr)2CoO4-δ, for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
